channel.title: How do I open this file?
channel.description:

Thanks you

item.title: How do I open this file?
item.dc:creator: @Javacisnotrecognized _^_
item.description:
@Javacisnotrecognized wrote:

You Don’t open the class files. You use java -

Like if it was Server.class you’d start it with Java Server

Here’s an example

java sun.applet.Main "http://ul7.runescape.com/lang/en/aff/runescape/game.ws?plugin=2"
